==English==
===Etymology===
From the idea of buying a T-shirt at a place visited as a tourist in order to show others that one has been to that place

===Idiom===
'''[[been]] [[there]], [[done]] [[that]], [[bought]] the [[T-shirt]]'''

#(''jocular'') Expresses the speaker's complete [[familiarity]] with a situation, with overtones of [[cynicism]] or [[exhaustion]].  Abbreviation (in Internet usage): '''[[BTDTBTTS]]'''

====Forms and variants====
*[[been there, done that]]
*[[been there, done that, got the T-shirt]]